{"tid":749661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葵翠邨鉛水事件 黃碧雲斥陳帆言論涼薄","createTime":"2018-07-20T08:18:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T16:04:52.000Z","uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"72704732e1c772a74c5cfccde6aff39c036c3e43","tid":749661,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T08:18:26.000Z","msg":"入伙兩個多月的葵涌葵翠邨，被民主黨驗出有3個食水樣本含鉛量超出世衛標準，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>運輸及房屋局長陳帆稱，葵翠邨食水達標，如住戶擔心，可選擇輪候其他屋邨</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員黃碧雲批評陳帆的講法涼薄、不負責任，沒有考慮居民感受。她又表示，雖然在入伙前抽驗的水辦顯示含鉛量合格，但質疑在承建商取樣過程中，房署和水務署沒有派人監視，不排除有人為因素影響驗水結果。"},{"pid":"36ffa5128083a1ae037480d5e67b5e2c120e9b2c","tid":749661,"uid":78791,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T08:19:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73f673b4867f14858d8df812f10db3542552dced","tid":749661,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T08:21:44.000Z","msg":"黃碧雲唔使教書咩？反應咁快嘅？"},{"pid":"7ab91c086a72d0e74602a70b0384b12c79df18ec","tid":749661,"uid":53421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:25:51.000Z","msg":"屌 未又係班新香港人<br />\n由鳩佢地喇"},{"pid":"0c3ec0948986224968d49aba8910b99502f5f93e","tid":749661,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T09:27:43.000Z","msg":"再換都係鉛水<br />\nd水喉匠永遠都拉唔完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa65db89602a01504d7df984c3936d5023390385","tid":749661,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"正宗「你唔鍾意香港，可以移民」翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd931186c17ac5759a6be2fd901b93f29826515","tid":749661,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T12:57:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"296371be12054768bd4cba297bde9ed1d8feefa8","tid":749661,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:04:52.000Z","msg":"陳帆好波<img 